# Guardrails

Load and apply before writes:

- `guardrails/transaction-safety.yaml` — value thresholds, gas limits, reorg depth
- `guardrails/security.yaml` — blind signing block, honeypot/rug detection
- `guardrails/compliance.yaml` — OFAC sanctions (no override), travel rule
- `guardrails/denied-topics.yaml` — block exploit/sanctions-evasion requests
